---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Company | Time Biotechnologies, Inc.">
    <Header />

    <main>
        <div class="page-header">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Company</h1>
                <p>Corporate Philosophy</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container page-content">
            <section class="section-block">
                <h2 class="slogan">
                    Building the foundation of time<br />with iPS technology
                </h2>
                <p class="slogan-sub">
                    Creating the foundation of time with iPS technology.
                </p>
            </section>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <section class="section-block">
                <div class="vmv-block">
                    <h2>Vision</h2>
                    <div class="vmv-content">
                        <p>
                            By integrating, editing, and restructuring all
                            scientific technologies,<br />
                            we aim to establish a drug discovery platform for complex
                            and unresolved issues of neurodegenerative diseases,<br
                            />
                            and give back the results to society.<br />
                            Accumulating past knowledge and looking ahead to future
                            possibilities,<br />
                            what matters is this very momentâ€”facing the disease, implementing
                            technology, and connecting it to treatment.<br />
                            From disease modeling to screening,<br />
                            and to the creation of diverse modalities such as compounds,
                            antibodies, nucleic acids, and cells,<br />
                            we push the boundaries of drug discovery centered on iPS
                            technology<br />
                            and show a realistic path to overcoming neurodegenerative
                            diseases.<br />
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="vmv-block">
                    <h2>Mission</h2>
                    <div class="vmv-content">
                        <p>
                            For diseases where establishing fundamental
                            treatments is difficult,<br />
                            we build and advance a drug discovery process based on
                            iPS technology,<br />
                            ensuring the path to treatment.<br />
                            We create models that capture the essence of the disease,
                            conduct screening to determine efficacy,<br />
                            and present diverse treatment means as realistic options.<br
                            />
                            By reconnecting fragments of research and technology and
                            converting them into the practice of drug discovery,<br
                            />
                            we create a meaningful "Present".<br />
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="vmv-block">
                    <h2>Value</h2>
                    <div class="vmv-content">
                        <p>
                            Time is not an abstract concept but a concrete
                            resource that can be converted into treatment.<br />
                            By deeply understanding the "heaven-sent" technology of
                            iPS, editing it for implementation,<br />
                            and using it fully in the appropriate form, we constantly
                            connect research to the field.<br />
                            Accumulating the activities and decisions to be made now<br
                            />
                            continues to support the "Time" that spins people's lives.<br
                            />
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-header {
        background-color: var(--c-gray-50);
        padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .page-header p {
        color: var(--c-gray-500);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .page-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 6rem;
    }

    .section-block {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .slogan {
        font-size: 2rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .slogan-sub {
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--c-gray-500);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background-color: var(--c-gray-200);
        margin: 4rem auto;
        width: 60px;
    }

    .vmv-block {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .vmv-block h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--c-accent);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--c-gray-100);
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .vmv-content {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.9;
        color: var(--c-gray-800);
    }

    .value-list li {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
</style>
